1
00:01:25,980 --> 00:01:34,920
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

2
00:01:35,330 --> 00:01:37,930
[Episode 25]

3
00:01:38,450 --> 00:01:39,259
Like I said,

4
00:01:40,090 --> 00:01:41,759
every play has its own fate.

5
00:01:42,340 --> 00:01:47,070
[The Late Love Filming Team]

6
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,979
No matter how unacceptable it is,

7
00:01:45,850 --> 00:01:47,050
you have to accept it.

8
00:01:49,930 --> 00:01:51,330
I just don't understand.

9
00:01:51,870 --> 00:01:57,160
[The Late Love Filming Team]

10
00:01:52,500 --> 00:01:53,500
How come everything seems

11
00:01:53,500 --> 00:01:55,030
to have changed overnight?

12
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:57,740
Actually,

13
00:01:58,900 --> 00:01:59,880
every change

14
00:01:59,950 --> 00:02:01,480
leaves a trace.

15
00:02:01,570 --> 00:02:02,480
Come on, sit down.

16
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:02,930
Sit.

17
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:07,860
[The Late Love Filming Team]

18
00:02:08,250 --> 00:02:10,449
Ever since he asked us to take out a loan,

19
00:02:10,630 --> 00:02:11,470
we've been having doubts

20
00:02:11,470 --> 00:02:12,970
the entire time, haven't we?

21
00:02:12,970 --> 00:02:13,860
However,

22
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,460
our obsession

23
00:02:15,460 --> 00:02:16,470
with this project

24
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:18,750
has outweighed all the uncertainties.

25
00:02:18,750 --> 00:02:20,410
If we were to start over again,

26
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:22,150
we'd still have to
go with the same option.

27
00:02:22,150 --> 00:02:22,620
So,

28
00:02:23,780 --> 00:02:25,520
we must face the consequences.

29
00:02:26,870 --> 00:02:27,829
In fact,

30
00:02:28,300 --> 00:02:29,510
in one's life,

31
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:31,329
if there are a few things

32
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:33,000
that one knows to be fiery pits

33
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,460
but still gladly jumps in,

34
00:02:34,650 --> 00:02:37,280
it's not necessarily a bad thing, is it?

35
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:39,800
Director! Director!

36
00:02:40,010 --> 00:02:42,100
["The Late Love"
Filming Team–Producer's Office]

37
00:02:41,340 --> 00:02:42,260
Director,

38
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:44,650
the entire crew is asking me for money.

39
00:02:45,030 --> 00:02:47,090
My pager is exploding with messages.

40
00:02:47,370 --> 00:02:48,150
I dare not return

41
00:02:48,150 --> 00:02:49,350
a single call.

42
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:51,280
What should we do about this?

43
00:02:52,579 --> 00:02:53,329
Pay them.

44
00:02:53,490 --> 00:02:57,170
[The Late Love Filming Team]

45
00:02:53,630 --> 00:02:55,329
We must pay them up.

46
00:02:56,030 --> 00:02:57,430
Come home with me now.

47
00:02:57,710 --> 00:02:59,620
I'll take money out
from my deposit account.

48
00:02:59,620 --> 00:02:59,970
Okay.

49
00:02:59,970 --> 00:03:00,800
Do some calculation.

50
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:02,060
Find out what payments

51
00:03:02,180 --> 00:03:04,030
must be made by the end of this month.

52
00:03:04,030 --> 00:03:04,780
Okay, got it.

53
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:15,620
Hello?

54
00:03:16,280 --> 00:03:17,530
Hello, Zhuang Zhuang.

55
00:03:17,530 --> 00:03:19,300
I was busy just now. What's up?

56
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:21,680
How's the movie preparation going?

57
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,010
Pretty good.

58
00:03:23,460 --> 00:03:24,920
The staff are all in place.

59
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,770
Once the next loan arrives,

60
00:03:26,860 --> 00:03:28,090
we'll start shooting.

61
00:03:28,090 --> 00:03:29,150
Director Weng said

62
00:03:29,370 --> 00:03:31,430
the cast all think highly of the script.

63
00:03:31,430 --> 00:03:33,310
That Hong Kong celebrity you're fond of

64
00:03:33,310 --> 00:03:34,440
will come do a cameo.

65
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:36,240
I'll get you an autograph then.

66
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:36,920
Okay.

67
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:40,079
Mr. Ye and your mom must be overjoyed

68
00:03:40,079 --> 00:03:41,410
to have you home, right?

69
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:47,079
When are you coming back?

70
00:03:47,130 --> 00:03:47,780
I'll go pick you up.

71
00:03:47,780 --> 00:03:49,840
I need to stay here for another while.

72
00:03:50,310 --> 00:03:52,770
Will you make it in time
for the competition?

73
00:03:52,900 --> 00:03:54,340
Yes, I will. Don't worry.

74
00:03:55,870 --> 00:03:56,329
Okay.

75
00:03:57,180 --> 00:03:59,370
Remember to practice singing
when you have time.

76
00:03:59,370 --> 00:04:00,880
Also, come back early.

77
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:01,780
When you're sure of the time,

78
00:04:01,780 --> 00:04:02,560
just let me know.

79
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:04,420
I'll check on the tickets for you.

80
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:05,950
Okay, I got it.

81
00:04:06,130 --> 00:04:07,400
I have to hang up now.

82
00:04:07,430 --> 00:04:09,130
T-Take care of yourself.

83
00:04:10,230 --> 00:04:10,700
Okay.

84
00:04:21,769 --> 00:04:22,560
We understand

85
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:24,090
how you must feel right now.

86
00:04:24,220 --> 00:04:25,420
But the cancer treatment process

87
00:04:25,420 --> 00:04:26,480
is indeed lengthy.

88
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:28,100
In particular, your mother's condition

89
00:04:28,100 --> 00:04:30,160
is more complicated than we thought.

90
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:31,610
I'm a daughter too.

91
00:04:31,950 --> 00:04:32,890
See, with you back home,

92
00:04:32,890 --> 00:04:34,350
your mother is very happy.

93
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:36,430
This is of great help to her condition.

94
00:04:36,430 --> 00:04:37,270
So, as her daughter,

95
00:04:37,270 --> 00:04:38,100
don't be disheartened.

96
00:04:38,100 --> 00:04:40,500
Spend more time with her
and encourage her.

97
00:04:41,930 --> 00:04:42,659
Stay strong.

98
00:04:43,130 --> 00:04:44,510
Let's all do our best together.

99
00:04:44,510 --> 00:04:45,770
-I got it.
-Go back now.

100
00:04:46,170 --> 00:04:49,920
[No smoking in public areas]

101
00:05:06,210 --> 00:05:08,570
[The Late Love]

102
00:05:19,370 --> 00:05:20,300
Don't be afraid.

103
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,260
I've asked the doctor.

104
00:05:22,660 --> 00:05:24,010
You'll fall asleep after the anesthesia.

105
00:05:24,010 --> 00:05:26,070
Then all will be fine when you wake up.

106
00:05:26,390 --> 00:05:27,450
With you by my side,

107
00:05:28,300 --> 00:05:29,960
I definitely won't be afraid.

108
00:05:31,950 --> 00:05:33,070
I'll go get some hot water

109
00:05:33,070 --> 00:05:34,000
to help you wash up.

110
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:34,930
There's no rush.

111
00:05:37,130 --> 00:05:38,540
Fetch me my bag

112
00:05:38,540 --> 00:05:39,470
from the closet.

113
00:05:45,310 --> 00:05:46,370
It's the one on top.

114
00:05:51,250 --> 00:05:52,310
What's in it?

115
00:05:56,420 --> 00:05:57,840
Previously,

116
00:05:58,370 --> 00:05:59,830
when I was feeling better,

117
00:06:00,270 --> 00:06:01,930
I made you some clothes.

118
00:06:09,890 --> 00:06:11,250
I made this costume for you

119
00:06:11,250 --> 00:06:12,560
to wear on stage.

120
00:06:23,890 --> 00:06:24,780
And this one...

121
00:06:25,430 --> 00:06:27,480
is for you to wear on your wedding.

122
00:06:59,120 --> 00:06:59,900
Is it pretty?

123
00:07:03,130 --> 00:07:03,690
Yes.

124
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:15,400
I've noticed you've gotten thinner again.

125
00:07:15,500 --> 00:07:16,550
I'm not sure

126
00:07:16,950 --> 00:07:18,880
if these dresses will fit you well.

127
00:07:19,270 --> 00:07:21,000
Alter them yourself if needed.

128
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:24,670
No, I won't.

129
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:26,740
I'll wait till you recover

130
00:07:26,740 --> 00:07:27,870
before I try them on.

131
00:07:28,180 --> 00:07:28,980
If they don't fit,

132
00:07:28,980 --> 00:07:30,710
I'll have you alter them for me.

133
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:38,240
Okay.

134
00:07:40,180 --> 00:07:41,510
I'll alter them for you.

135
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:31,510
The last time you lay beside me

136
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:34,159
in a hospital bed like this,

137
00:08:36,100 --> 00:08:38,059
you were a chubby,

138
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:39,500
soft little baby

139
00:08:40,390 --> 00:08:43,500
who smiled at the sight of me.

140
00:08:46,530 --> 00:08:47,660
Little did I imagine

141
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:50,310
you'd grow up so fast

142
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:52,080
into an extraordinary lady.

143
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:56,250
You've only seen a fraction

144
00:08:56,250 --> 00:08:57,510
of what I'm capable of.

145
00:09:00,910 --> 00:09:02,890
After you're discharged from the hospital,

146
00:09:02,890 --> 00:09:03,650
I'll show you

147
00:09:03,650 --> 00:09:05,350
the movie I took part in.

148
00:09:07,010 --> 00:09:08,870
I played a great Shanghai singer.

149
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:10,060
Splendid, I'd say.

150
00:09:13,370 --> 00:09:14,950
I also designed a dress,

151
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:17,420
but the drawing was nearly snatched.

152
00:09:18,250 --> 00:09:20,110
Luckily, I fought and got it back.

153
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:21,200
I'm waiting

154
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:23,000
for you to make that dress for me.

155
00:09:31,910 --> 00:09:33,720
What was the song

156
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:34,770
you said I'd smile at

157
00:09:34,770 --> 00:09:35,970
whenever you sang it?

158
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:37,550
Sing it to me again.

159
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:46,630
Go to sleep,

160
00:09:47,550 --> 00:09:51,410
my dear baby.

161
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:55,840
Sleep tight,

162
00:09:56,650 --> 00:09:59,860
Mommy loves you.

163
00:10:01,460 --> 00:10:05,700
Go to sleep,

164
00:10:06,650 --> 00:10:09,820
my dear baby.

165
00:10:13,750 --> 00:10:14,250
Uncle,

166
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:16,820
if you're feeling unwell lately,

167
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:17,790
just let me

168
00:10:17,790 --> 00:10:19,340
do your bidding.

169
00:10:19,870 --> 00:10:21,080
I'll keep the accounts

170
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:22,530
clear and show them

171
00:10:22,670 --> 00:10:24,070
to you on a regular basis.

172
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:25,440
If I have questions,

173
00:10:25,500 --> 00:10:26,830
I'll ask you for advice.

174
00:10:27,460 --> 00:10:28,150
Okay, okay.

175
00:10:30,150 --> 00:10:31,000
I trust you.

176
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:36,490
Why don't you give me a smile?

177
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:38,260
Because I'm still feeling...

178
00:10:38,820 --> 00:10:40,010
a bit worried.

179
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:41,100
Look at you.

180
00:10:42,390 --> 00:10:44,240
It's the same old problem again.

181
00:10:44,870 --> 00:10:47,310
Cao Ye, I'm not criticizing you.

182
00:10:48,050 --> 00:10:49,790
But look out on the streets.

183
00:10:51,010 --> 00:10:52,500
Everyone's mind

184
00:10:52,520 --> 00:10:54,250
is far from simple.

185
00:10:54,630 --> 00:10:55,410
Who isn't

186
00:10:55,410 --> 00:10:57,200
sharp as a tack?

187
00:10:58,010 --> 00:10:59,870
You get bullied when you are weak.

188
00:11:00,630 --> 00:11:02,130
But when you are strong,

189
00:11:02,500 --> 00:11:04,770
everyone will smile at you.

190
00:11:08,270 --> 00:11:09,270
Wake up

191
00:11:10,270 --> 00:11:11,200
from your dream.

192
00:11:17,100 --> 00:11:17,770
Cui,

193
00:11:19,010 --> 00:11:20,220
thank you so much

194
00:11:20,700 --> 00:11:23,030
for all you've done for me
over these days.

195
00:11:23,580 --> 00:11:24,100
Ranran,

196
00:11:25,130 --> 00:11:27,190
are you sure you won't reconsider it?

197
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:29,980
It's a wonderful role

198
00:11:29,980 --> 00:11:31,310
of a wonderful project.

199
00:11:31,370 --> 00:11:33,150
Everyone's fighting tooth and nail for it.

200
00:11:33,150 --> 00:11:34,080
See, you've just

201
00:11:34,270 --> 00:11:36,010
embarked on the journey
to a bright future.

202
00:11:36,010 --> 00:11:36,410
Why...

203
00:11:36,790 --> 00:11:38,410
why do you have to quit?

204
00:11:38,750 --> 00:11:39,520
Cui,

205
00:11:40,820 --> 00:11:42,130
I remember you saying

206
00:11:42,820 --> 00:11:45,080
that good luck only favors the capable.

207
00:11:47,290 --> 00:11:48,750
I don't think I'm capable enough

208
00:11:48,750 --> 00:11:50,220
to embrace such good luck.

209
00:11:50,770 --> 00:11:52,130
Even if I do,

210
00:11:52,630 --> 00:11:53,890
it won't serve me well.

211
00:11:54,340 --> 00:11:56,030
If I keep moving on like this,

212
00:11:57,240 --> 00:11:58,080
I'm afraid I'll really

213
00:11:58,080 --> 00:11:58,960
forget who I am.

214
00:12:01,120 --> 00:12:02,450
Chu Caiyuan

215
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:03,850
is a married man,

216
00:12:03,910 --> 00:12:05,910
yet he's still looking for affairs.

217
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:07,690
-I really think...
-He and I...

218
00:12:08,250 --> 00:12:10,310
will never ever get in contact again.

219
00:12:11,510 --> 00:12:12,640
It's all in the past.

220
00:12:16,810 --> 00:12:18,350
L-Let's not talk about him.

221
00:12:38,340 --> 00:12:39,600
For the sake of acting,

222
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:41,340
I've suffered,

223
00:12:42,530 --> 00:12:43,860
swallowed grievances,

224
00:12:44,510 --> 00:12:45,460
and complained.

225
00:12:47,750 --> 00:12:48,740
But, Cui,

226
00:12:50,870 --> 00:12:52,870
if everyone in this industry

227
00:12:53,510 --> 00:12:55,910
needs to find a backer
before getting a job,

228
00:12:56,580 --> 00:12:58,110
don't you think it is wrong?

229
00:12:59,440 --> 00:13:00,930
If I rise to fame from this,

230
00:13:01,890 --> 00:13:03,620
then which poor actress like me

231
00:13:04,120 --> 00:13:05,340
has lost her chance to play the part

232
00:13:05,340 --> 00:13:06,010
I've got?

233
00:13:08,550 --> 00:13:09,690
I understand...

234
00:13:10,130 --> 00:13:11,260
what you're saying.

235
00:13:11,960 --> 00:13:12,690
Ranran,

236
00:13:13,220 --> 00:13:14,880
you are really different now.

237
00:13:17,580 --> 00:13:19,110
I'm leaving this industry.

238
00:13:20,100 --> 00:13:21,200
That means we won't get to

239
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:22,130
meet up as often.

240
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:23,970
I pray for you to find

241
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:26,380
a suitable path for yourself.

242
00:13:27,290 --> 00:13:29,270
Remember? In a previous auction,

243
00:13:30,390 --> 00:13:32,990
I couldn't get into character
however I tried.

244
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:34,270
But I caught on to it right away

245
00:13:34,270 --> 00:13:35,890
as you gave me an instruction.

246
00:13:35,890 --> 00:13:37,080
Don't you think...

247
00:13:37,290 --> 00:13:38,950
you have a gift for directing?

248
00:13:42,410 --> 00:13:43,270
Thank you.

249
00:13:43,740 --> 00:13:44,370
Well...

250
00:13:44,790 --> 00:13:45,720
I'll try my best.

251
00:13:45,890 --> 00:13:46,860
I really mean it.

252
00:13:46,860 --> 00:13:47,360
Yeah.

253
00:13:50,290 --> 00:13:50,960
Ranran,

254
00:13:51,890 --> 00:13:52,940
what do you plan

255
00:13:53,530 --> 00:13:54,860
to do in the future then?

256
00:13:57,650 --> 00:13:59,450
I don't want to go back to Huzhou.

257
00:14:01,270 --> 00:14:02,740
Now, I have found a job

258
00:14:02,740 --> 00:14:04,070
as a preschool teacher.

259
00:14:05,170 --> 00:14:06,530
I'll live my life well.

260
00:14:08,670 --> 00:14:09,400
That's good.

261
00:14:10,750 --> 00:14:14,270
[Scouting photos] [Character settings]

262
00:14:11,870 --> 00:14:13,670
As part of the filming industry,

263
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:15,580
it's heartbreaking to see it lose

264
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:18,010
such a good, dedicated

265
00:14:18,550 --> 00:14:20,370
and hardworking actress.

266
00:14:20,930 --> 00:14:22,530
But as a good friend of yours,

267
00:14:22,820 --> 00:14:23,820
I'm happy for you.

268
00:14:24,630 --> 00:14:25,320
I'm glad...

269
00:14:26,030 --> 00:14:27,100
that your heart is still

270
00:14:27,100 --> 00:14:27,960
as pure as ever

271
00:14:28,270 --> 00:14:30,600
after a journey through this vanity fair.

272
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:34,260
I'll also pray for you.

273
00:14:36,700 --> 00:14:37,960
I wish you all the best.

274
00:14:39,170 --> 00:14:39,900
Absolutely.

275
00:14:40,700 --> 00:14:41,600
That was an impression of me.

276
00:14:41,600 --> 00:14:42,500
Was it spot-on?

277
00:14:42,750 --> 00:14:43,410
Not really.

278
00:14:47,960 --> 00:14:48,710
Liangliang!

279
00:14:49,510 --> 00:14:50,040
Liang...

280
00:14:50,960 --> 00:14:52,730
Why are you still sleeping?

281
00:14:52,820 --> 00:14:53,460
Get up!

282
00:14:53,600 --> 00:14:54,600
Come cook with me.

283
00:14:54,670 --> 00:14:55,580
We'll have drinks later.

284
00:14:55,580 --> 00:14:56,440
Come on, get up.

285
00:14:56,820 --> 00:14:57,880
Alright, Zongbao.

286
00:14:57,980 --> 00:14:59,110
You go do your thing.

287
00:14:59,150 --> 00:15:00,950
Let me have some quiet time here.

288
00:15:03,250 --> 00:15:04,840
What's going on with you?

289
00:15:06,910 --> 00:15:09,740
You've been doing business with Xiaojun

290
00:15:09,740 --> 00:15:10,960
lately.

291
00:15:11,320 --> 00:15:11,770
Why...

292
00:15:12,270 --> 00:15:14,340
do you look so listless?

293
00:15:15,580 --> 00:15:16,710
Come on.

294
00:15:17,170 --> 00:15:18,080
I'm a grown man

295
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:18,840
who has worked his tail off

296
00:15:18,840 --> 00:15:19,630
without earning even a penny.

297
00:15:19,630 --> 00:15:20,760
How could I be happy?

298
00:15:23,550 --> 00:15:26,200
So you're worried that Ranran
might suffer with you

299
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:28,330
since you haven't made any money, huh?

300
00:15:28,720 --> 00:15:30,410
Enough. Drop this subject.

301
00:15:30,410 --> 00:15:31,630
Just go do your thing.

302
00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:35,050
You're not in the right state.

303
00:15:35,940 --> 00:15:36,410
Get up!

304
00:15:37,940 --> 00:15:39,250
I said get up! Did you hear?

305
00:15:39,250 --> 00:15:40,620
Just go do your thing.

306
00:15:40,620 --> 00:15:42,120
Leave me alone.

307
00:15:44,050 --> 00:15:45,130
Hey,

308
00:15:46,130 --> 00:15:48,220
look where I stand now.

309
00:15:49,050 --> 00:15:49,850
For one thing,

310
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:51,770
I have no money.

311
00:15:52,650 --> 00:15:54,740
For another, I have no background.

312
00:15:55,030 --> 00:15:56,200
But think about it.

313
00:15:56,940 --> 00:15:58,140
My wife and I

314
00:15:58,320 --> 00:15:59,600
are living

315
00:16:00,290 --> 00:16:02,200
a more and more enjoyable life.

316
00:16:04,860 --> 00:16:05,670
Why is that?

317
00:16:11,620 --> 00:16:13,390
Then please explain to me

318
00:16:13,390 --> 00:16:14,790
why things are picking up

319
00:16:15,390 --> 00:16:16,350
for you

320
00:16:16,790 --> 00:16:18,030
and your wife.

321
00:16:18,170 --> 00:16:18,750
First,

322
00:16:20,480 --> 00:16:21,960
I have a sincere heart.

323
00:16:23,000 --> 00:16:23,460
Second,

324
00:16:24,370 --> 00:16:25,890
for my wife

325
00:16:26,630 --> 00:16:27,340
and son,

326
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:30,080
I can work my fingers to the bone, right?

327
00:16:30,080 --> 00:16:30,610
Third...

328
00:16:30,890 --> 00:16:32,530
Alright, stop it.

329
00:16:32,630 --> 00:16:34,090
I have a sincere heart too,

330
00:16:34,120 --> 00:16:35,360
and I can also work hard.

331
00:16:35,360 --> 00:16:36,460
But I don't have money!

332
00:16:36,460 --> 00:16:37,420
How can hard work

333
00:16:37,620 --> 00:16:39,460
and a sincere heart
be compared with money?

334
00:16:39,460 --> 00:16:41,200
I want to help Ranran realize her dream.

335
00:16:41,200 --> 00:16:42,170
I hate to see her

336
00:16:42,170 --> 00:16:43,370
sitting in that Lincoln.

337
00:16:43,370 --> 00:16:45,170
But what can I do when I'm so poor?

338
00:16:45,790 --> 00:16:47,450
Okay, alright, I understand.

339
00:16:50,050 --> 00:16:50,780
Liangliang.

340
00:16:52,670 --> 00:16:55,030
You can't keep being like this.

341
00:16:56,460 --> 00:16:58,330
You are like a brother

342
00:16:58,770 --> 00:16:59,720
to us.

343
00:17:00,700 --> 00:17:01,320
However,

344
00:17:01,340 --> 00:17:03,350
in front of Ranran,

345
00:17:03,980 --> 00:17:05,900
you must act like a real man.

346
00:17:06,500 --> 00:17:08,550
How long have we known Ranran?

347
00:17:09,569 --> 00:17:11,770
You're well aware of what kind of person

348
00:17:11,940 --> 00:17:13,000
she is, aren't you?

349
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:15,970
Don't obsess over

350
00:17:16,290 --> 00:17:17,810
what you need to become

351
00:17:17,810 --> 00:17:19,210
just to give her the best.

352
00:17:19,420 --> 00:17:20,680
You should think about

353
00:17:20,900 --> 00:17:22,300
what Ranran really needs

354
00:17:22,530 --> 00:17:23,589
in her inner heart.

355
00:17:28,290 --> 00:17:30,610
Try not to let your pride

356
00:17:31,240 --> 00:17:32,940
hold you back.

357
00:17:33,960 --> 00:17:34,550
Okay?

358
00:17:36,220 --> 00:17:37,420
Give it some thought.

359
00:17:39,290 --> 00:17:40,340
I'm going to cook.

360
00:17:40,720 --> 00:17:42,880
Love is conveyed through cooking.

361
00:17:44,020 --> 00:17:46,220
I'll let you know when the food's ready.

362
00:17:46,680 --> 00:17:48,280
We'll have drinks, alright?

363
00:18:13,020 --> 00:18:19,370
[Surgery in Progress]

364
00:18:19,440 --> 00:18:24,430
[Operating Theater]

365
00:18:24,480 --> 00:18:34,110
[Surgery in Progress]

366
00:18:34,170 --> 00:18:42,030
[Operating Theater]

367
00:18:39,350 --> 00:18:40,400
During surgery, we found

368
00:18:40,400 --> 00:18:41,460
the patient's tumor is so large

369
00:18:41,460 --> 00:18:41,960
that it is

370
00:18:41,960 --> 00:18:43,610
compressing an artery in the lungs.

371
00:18:43,610 --> 00:18:44,480
Continuing the operation

372
00:18:44,480 --> 00:18:45,380
would greatly increase health risks.

373
00:18:45,380 --> 00:18:46,700
So we had to terminate it.

374
00:18:46,700 --> 00:18:48,420
T-Then where do we go from here?

375
00:18:48,420 --> 00:18:48,830
Next,

376
00:18:48,830 --> 00:18:50,400
we will arrange
radiotherapy and chemotherapy

377
00:18:50,400 --> 00:18:51,200
for the patient

378
00:18:51,200 --> 00:18:52,480
to shrink the tumor.

379
00:18:52,610 --> 00:18:54,470
Only then can we devise new plans.

380
00:18:56,310 --> 00:19:00,150
[Operating Theater]

381
00:19:04,720 --> 00:19:08,670
[Operating Theater]

382
00:19:29,880 --> 00:19:34,640
[Chinese Folk Music]

383
00:19:33,110 --> 00:19:34,790
You have a solid foundation in singing.

384
00:19:34,790 --> 00:19:35,590
Rest assured, Mr. Zheng.

385
00:19:35,590 --> 00:19:36,030
I will

386
00:19:36,030 --> 00:19:37,760
practice as often as possible.

387
00:19:41,310 --> 00:19:42,640
Beijing is full of talented people.

388
00:19:42,640 --> 00:19:44,250
The competition will be very fierce.

389
00:19:44,250 --> 00:19:45,250
Can you handle it?

390
00:19:45,610 --> 00:19:46,210
Yes, I can.

391
00:19:46,780 --> 00:19:48,860
[Notice of participation
in the National Singer Competition]

392
00:19:50,220 --> 00:19:51,620
The finalist list is out.

393
00:19:51,750 --> 00:19:53,410
You made it to the finals.

394
00:19:53,460 --> 00:19:54,160
You are now

395
00:19:54,160 --> 00:19:56,420
getting closer and closer to your dream.

396
00:20:18,200 --> 00:20:18,900
Hello, this is

397
00:20:18,900 --> 00:20:22,430
the organizing committee
of the National Singer Competition.

398
00:20:22,700 --> 00:20:23,400
Hello,

399
00:20:23,400 --> 00:20:26,000
this is Zhuang Zhuang,
one of the contestants.

400
00:20:26,680 --> 00:20:27,140
Hello.

401
00:20:27,350 --> 00:20:28,510
How may I help you?

402
00:20:33,720 --> 00:20:35,180
I've decided to withdraw.

403
00:20:38,770 --> 00:20:39,920
Are you sure?

404
00:20:45,480 --> 00:20:46,280
Yes, I'm sure.

405
00:20:46,550 --> 00:20:47,680
Sorry for quitting.

406
00:21:58,590 --> 00:21:59,530
Hello.

407
00:22:00,010 --> 00:22:01,870
Zhuang Zhuang, it's me, Shengli.

408
00:22:01,920 --> 00:22:03,920
Why haven't I heard from you lately?

409
00:22:03,960 --> 00:22:05,090
Is everything okay?

410
00:22:07,180 --> 00:22:08,640
The shooting has started.

411
00:22:08,680 --> 00:22:09,410
Don't worry.

412
00:22:10,110 --> 00:22:11,880
Have you filmed the scenes
you told me about

413
00:22:11,880 --> 00:22:12,720
earlier?

414
00:22:13,770 --> 00:22:14,700
Yes, all of them.

415
00:22:15,110 --> 00:22:17,110
Everything's going very smoothly.

416
00:22:17,510 --> 00:22:19,680
Director Weng is amazing.

417
00:22:20,000 --> 00:22:21,640
I've been watching him turning texts

418
00:22:21,640 --> 00:22:22,660
into pictures.

419
00:22:23,010 --> 00:22:24,270
It's really exciting.

420
00:22:24,310 --> 00:22:25,000
That day, after shooting,

421
00:22:25,000 --> 00:22:26,790
he even asked me to watch the editing.

422
00:22:26,790 --> 00:22:28,610
I went to the editing room, took a look,

423
00:22:28,610 --> 00:22:29,870
and was really amazed.

424
00:22:30,530 --> 00:22:32,460
He also told me to stay with the crew

425
00:22:32,570 --> 00:22:34,590
to do some script revision work.

426
00:22:38,000 --> 00:22:40,260
What about you? When are you coming back?

427
00:22:40,330 --> 00:22:41,010
Won't

428
00:22:41,050 --> 00:22:42,850
the competition commence soon?

429
00:22:45,110 --> 00:22:46,000
I did some thinking

430
00:22:46,000 --> 00:22:47,220
and decided to quit.

431
00:22:50,110 --> 00:22:52,440
When I attended the preliminary contest,

432
00:22:52,460 --> 00:22:54,440
I found my rivals all highly professional

433
00:22:54,440 --> 00:22:55,500
and better than me.

434
00:22:55,830 --> 00:22:58,000
There's no point in going for the finals.

435
00:22:58,000 --> 00:22:59,330
Are you nervous or what?

436
00:23:00,610 --> 00:23:02,010
I'm sure all will be fine.

437
00:23:02,270 --> 00:23:03,550
You're an excellent singer.

438
00:23:03,550 --> 00:23:05,950
You'll definitely outperform the others.

439
00:23:11,500 --> 00:23:11,900
Hello?

440
00:23:14,880 --> 00:23:16,010
Hey, Zhuang Zhuang?

441
00:23:17,110 --> 00:23:18,640
Why don't you say anything?

442
00:23:19,700 --> 00:23:20,100
Are...

443
00:23:21,180 --> 00:23:22,910
A-Are you sure about quitting?

444
00:23:23,740 --> 00:23:25,070
But why, Zhuang Zhuang?

445
00:23:25,810 --> 00:23:27,530
W-Why are you withdrawing?

446
00:23:27,830 --> 00:23:29,110
We've stuck it out so long in Beijing

447
00:23:29,110 --> 00:23:31,040
just to fulfill our dreams, right?

448
00:23:32,030 --> 00:23:33,090
The two of us worked

449
00:23:33,550 --> 00:23:35,480
from dawn to dusk selling clothes,

450
00:23:35,810 --> 00:23:36,290
and...

451
00:23:36,440 --> 00:23:37,640
we even went to Russia

452
00:23:37,880 --> 00:23:39,080
to resell clothes.

453
00:23:39,440 --> 00:23:40,070
We made all that effort

454
00:23:40,070 --> 00:23:42,200
just to survive in Beijing, didn't we?

455
00:23:42,250 --> 00:23:44,350
You're only one step away
from realizing your dream now.

456
00:23:44,350 --> 00:23:46,080
Why are you suddenly giving up?

457
00:23:48,310 --> 00:23:49,570
Hello, Zhuang Zhuang?

458
00:23:50,440 --> 00:23:51,970
Did anything happen to you?

459
00:23:53,160 --> 00:23:55,050
I'll come find you, Zhuang Zhuang.

460
00:23:55,050 --> 00:23:56,480
No, nothing happened.

461
00:24:00,940 --> 00:24:02,190
I'm perfectly fine.

462
00:24:04,480 --> 00:24:06,740
The shooting of your movie
has finally begun.

463
00:24:06,740 --> 00:24:08,600
Make sure you fulfill your dream.

464
00:24:08,680 --> 00:24:09,400
Zhuang Zhuang,

465
00:24:09,400 --> 00:24:11,060
your dream is my dream as well.

466
00:24:12,160 --> 00:24:14,160
Thank you for always supporting me.

467
00:24:14,550 --> 00:24:15,610
I sincerely hope

468
00:24:16,830 --> 00:24:17,290
your dream

469
00:24:17,290 --> 00:24:18,740
will come to a good end.

470
00:24:21,310 --> 00:24:21,980
I've made up my mind

471
00:24:21,980 --> 00:24:22,770
to quit the competition.

472
00:24:22,770 --> 00:24:24,010
Don't try to persuade me anymore.

473
00:24:24,010 --> 00:24:24,960
Zhuang Zhuang...

474
00:24:24,960 --> 00:24:28,220
-Zhuang Zhuang, you must not quit...
-Focus on your movie.

475
00:25:28,480 --> 00:25:29,150
Excuse me.

476
00:25:29,400 --> 00:25:30,980
No one's at Meiqin Tailor Shop.

477
00:25:30,980 --> 00:25:32,240
Do you know where the owner

478
00:25:32,240 --> 00:25:33,050
and her family live?

479
00:25:33,050 --> 00:25:33,930
And you are?

480
00:25:35,140 --> 00:25:36,050
I'm looking for her daughter,

481
00:25:36,050 --> 00:25:36,480
Zhuang Zhuang.

482
00:25:36,480 --> 00:25:39,610
Their address is No. 8, 69th Alley,
Shamao River Street.

483
00:25:44,550 --> 00:25:45,400
Who is it?

484
00:25:45,650 --> 00:25:47,250
It's me, Xu Shengli.

485
00:25:48,660 --> 00:25:49,520
Zhuang Zhuang?

486
00:25:49,570 --> 00:25:50,940
It's me, Shengli.

487
00:25:52,900 --> 00:25:53,760
Zhuang Zhuang?

488
00:25:54,440 --> 00:25:56,100
Zhuang Zhuang, open the door.

489
00:25:59,680 --> 00:26:00,540
Zhuang Zhuang.

490
00:26:09,220 --> 00:26:10,080
Zhuang Zhuang,

491
00:26:10,940 --> 00:26:12,330
can we have a word?

492
00:26:13,510 --> 00:26:14,910
Has something happened?

493
00:26:15,480 --> 00:26:16,810
You can tell me about it.

494
00:26:18,070 --> 00:26:19,870
As for the singing competition,

495
00:26:20,610 --> 00:26:21,200
under no circumstances

496
00:26:21,200 --> 00:26:22,530
should you give up on it.

497
00:26:23,570 --> 00:26:24,640
That's your dream.

498
00:26:25,420 --> 00:26:26,680
If you quit, then...

499
00:26:27,440 --> 00:26:28,200
my dream won't

500
00:26:28,200 --> 00:26:29,600
have any meaning either.

501
00:26:55,410 --> 00:27:00,610
♪ Grow wild like spring grass ♪

502
00:27:01,980 --> 00:27:09,220
♪ I embrace the galaxy
in the gentle evening breeze ♪

503
00:27:09,870 --> 00:27:13,530
♪ The sky slowly brightens into dawn ♪

504
00:27:14,070 --> 00:27:16,490
♪ Let me sing a song ♪

505
00:27:17,360 --> 00:27:20,090
♪ Unyielding even in cracks ♪

506
00:27:21,080 --> 00:27:29,400
♪ Wild grass thrives
in the lushness of spring ♪

507
00:27:37,070 --> 00:27:42,830
♪ The breeze knows and the dew knows ♪

508
00:27:43,990 --> 00:27:49,030
♪ That hometown is not a shelter
one can hide in forever ♪

509
00:27:50,960 --> 00:27:52,870
♪ Under the towering city walls ♪

510
00:27:52,680 --> 00:27:53,680
Zhuangzhuang, do you remember

511
00:27:53,330 --> 00:27:56,730
♪ In a corner of the northern sea ♪

512
00:27:53,740 --> 00:27:55,340
when you recorded this song,

513
00:27:55,700 --> 00:27:57,500
you were thrilled, weren't you?

514
00:27:57,950 --> 00:27:59,440
♪ And in places
where the sun doesn't shine ♪

515
00:27:59,530 --> 00:28:00,890
Are you being too nervous?

516
00:27:59,970 --> 00:28:02,510
♪ I've lingered and rested ♪

517
00:28:01,160 --> 00:28:02,760
Or are you just stressed out?

518
00:28:03,200 --> 00:28:03,880
It's okay.

519
00:28:04,220 --> 00:28:05,310
I will always be with you.

520
00:28:04,580 --> 00:28:10,010
♪ Towards the light,
I straighten my back ♪

521
00:28:05,920 --> 00:28:07,810
The result really doesn't matter,

522
00:28:07,810 --> 00:28:09,740
but at least we need to give it a try.

523
00:28:11,290 --> 00:28:16,910
♪ I must touch the clouds
however high the sky is ♪

524
00:28:18,610 --> 00:28:23,160
♪ Though I drift in the wind,
my heart remains unshaken ♪

525
00:28:23,140 --> 00:28:24,290
You're Shengli, right?

526
00:28:24,270 --> 00:28:26,300
♪ A ray of light will eventually ♪

527
00:28:26,140 --> 00:28:27,010
Mr. Ye.

528
00:28:27,290 --> 00:28:28,180
♪ Shed on me ♪

529
00:28:30,700 --> 00:28:32,710
What are you doing in Wenzhou?

530
00:28:33,590 --> 00:28:35,120
I'm here for Zhuang Zhuang.

531
00:28:37,160 --> 00:28:38,360
Her mother goes to bed

532
00:28:38,790 --> 00:28:39,640
early.

533
00:28:39,750 --> 00:28:41,460
She hasn't rested well lately.

534
00:28:41,460 --> 00:28:42,920
Please stop knocking at the door.

535
00:28:42,920 --> 00:28:44,050
It might wake her up.

536
00:28:47,750 --> 00:28:48,610
How about this?

537
00:28:48,770 --> 00:28:50,590
Go to the entrance to the alley and sit

538
00:28:50,590 --> 00:28:51,550
there for a while.

539
00:28:51,550 --> 00:28:54,100
I'll get in there, check on Zhuang Zhuang,

540
00:28:54,530 --> 00:28:56,330
and meet up with you later. Okay?

541
00:28:57,140 --> 00:28:58,470
Yes, sure.

542
00:28:58,790 --> 00:28:59,350
Mr. Ye,

543
00:28:59,830 --> 00:29:01,680
do try to persuade Zhuang Zhuang.

544
00:29:01,680 --> 00:29:02,220
She must not

545
00:29:02,220 --> 00:29:03,950
quit the singing competition.

546
00:29:04,250 --> 00:29:04,880
Got it.

547
00:29:05,220 --> 00:29:06,220
Thank you, Mr. Ye.

548
00:29:48,350 --> 00:29:49,210
Thanks, Mr. Ye.

549
00:30:04,590 --> 00:30:05,140
Kiddo,

550
00:30:07,160 --> 00:30:08,960
I know what you must be thinking.

551
00:30:11,810 --> 00:30:14,270
But I don't think you can hide the truth
from him forever,

552
00:30:14,270 --> 00:30:16,000
judging from how much he cares.

553
00:30:21,840 --> 00:30:23,640
I remember back in my childhood,

554
00:30:25,310 --> 00:30:27,510
when you first got together
with my mom,

555
00:30:27,850 --> 00:30:29,450
you were working out of town.

556
00:30:31,590 --> 00:30:33,320
Suppose at that time, my mom...

557
00:30:35,210 --> 00:30:35,740
my mom told you

558
00:30:35,740 --> 00:30:37,700
something serious happened at home,

559
00:30:37,700 --> 00:30:38,700
what would you do?

560
00:30:40,070 --> 00:30:42,200
I would definitely leave everything behind

561
00:30:42,200 --> 00:30:44,330
and come back to keep your mom company.

562
00:30:47,640 --> 00:30:49,570
Shengli is the same kind of person.

563
00:30:58,310 --> 00:30:59,710
Now, he is actually doing

564
00:31:00,480 --> 00:31:02,070
what he has always,

565
00:31:04,250 --> 00:31:05,450
always aspired to do.

566
00:31:06,070 --> 00:31:07,600
It's very important to him,

567
00:31:09,810 --> 00:31:10,750
just like how important

568
00:31:10,750 --> 00:31:12,610
the singing competition is to me.

569
00:31:14,310 --> 00:31:15,640
When a chance is missed,

570
00:31:16,790 --> 00:31:18,250
it might never come again.

571
00:31:27,400 --> 00:31:28,510
If I told him what our family

572
00:31:28,510 --> 00:31:30,040
is going through right now,

573
00:31:32,180 --> 00:31:33,460
he would by no means

574
00:31:33,460 --> 00:31:34,590
let me face it alone.

575
00:31:37,440 --> 00:31:38,530
No matter what,

576
00:31:39,380 --> 00:31:41,160
you must not hurt his feelings.

577
00:31:42,640 --> 00:31:43,970
Because when some words

578
00:31:45,090 --> 00:31:45,880
are said, they will

579
00:31:45,880 --> 00:31:47,140
cause eternal damage.

580
00:31:48,220 --> 00:31:49,710
That will be harm

581
00:31:50,270 --> 00:31:51,480
to both of you.

582
00:31:56,140 --> 00:31:58,340
No matter what you choose in the future,

583
00:31:58,620 --> 00:32:00,420
you have accompanied each other

584
00:32:01,350 --> 00:32:03,220
and given for each other.

585
00:32:04,030 --> 00:32:06,030
There's affection between you two.

586
00:32:13,110 --> 00:32:15,040
I don't know what the future holds.

587
00:32:26,030 --> 00:32:26,560
Alright.

588
00:32:29,010 --> 00:32:30,940
I know just what to tell him.

589
00:33:21,160 --> 00:33:21,750
Mr. Ye.

590
00:33:24,270 --> 00:33:25,030
Shengli,

591
00:33:26,270 --> 00:33:28,240
Zhuang Zhuang can't go with you.

592
00:33:31,880 --> 00:33:32,650
Then, Mr. Ye,

593
00:33:32,670 --> 00:33:33,820
can I see her?

594
00:33:34,720 --> 00:33:36,580
H-Has something happened to her?

595
00:33:36,700 --> 00:33:37,550
B-But no matter what,

596
00:33:37,550 --> 00:33:39,610
she can't give up on the competition.

597
00:33:40,700 --> 00:33:42,140
She refused to see you

598
00:33:42,720 --> 00:33:44,320
not because she is mad at you.

599
00:33:45,910 --> 00:33:47,710
She's just very upset right now.

600
00:33:48,240 --> 00:33:49,640
There are certain things

601
00:33:49,960 --> 00:33:52,050
she can't bring herself to say to you.

602
00:33:52,110 --> 00:33:53,570
I hope you can understand.

603
00:33:54,250 --> 00:33:56,100
As for the competition,

604
00:33:56,570 --> 00:33:57,970
that's her own business.

605
00:33:58,770 --> 00:34:00,610
You can't impose your ideas

606
00:34:00,960 --> 00:34:01,920
on her,

607
00:34:02,000 --> 00:34:03,060
and neither can we.

608
00:34:06,380 --> 00:34:07,010
Shengli,

609
00:34:08,880 --> 00:34:10,590
y-you're a nice young man.

610
00:34:12,630 --> 00:34:14,590
Your love for Zhuang Zhuang is genuine.

611
00:34:14,590 --> 00:34:16,170
I bet you can also feel

612
00:34:16,520 --> 00:34:18,520
that her love for you is genuine too.

613
00:34:20,230 --> 00:34:20,830
That said,

614
00:34:21,550 --> 00:34:23,949
you should show some understanding for us.

615
00:34:29,460 --> 00:34:30,380
Although Zhuang Zhuang is not

616
00:34:30,380 --> 00:34:31,780
my biological daughter,

617
00:34:31,900 --> 00:34:33,530
she's the only child I have,

618
00:34:33,900 --> 00:34:35,500
and I see her as my own.

619
00:34:36,130 --> 00:34:37,300
I've come to an age

620
00:34:38,000 --> 00:34:39,330
where I'd hate to see her

621
00:34:39,409 --> 00:34:41,590
drifting around out there all the time.

622
00:34:41,590 --> 00:34:42,639
On this point,

623
00:34:42,840 --> 00:34:44,969
I think your parents feel the same way.

624
00:34:46,610 --> 00:34:47,320
Mr. Ye,

625
00:34:48,010 --> 00:34:49,340
I don't know what exactly

626
00:34:49,340 --> 00:34:51,070
has gone wrong between me and her.

627
00:34:51,070 --> 00:34:51,670
Neither do I think

628
00:34:51,670 --> 00:34:52,420
anything has gone wrong

629
00:34:52,420 --> 00:34:53,480
between me and her.

630
00:34:54,210 --> 00:34:54,880
We've stayed

631
00:34:54,880 --> 00:34:55,760
and struggled for so long in Beijing

632
00:34:55,760 --> 00:34:57,420
just to realize our dreams, right?

633
00:34:57,420 --> 00:34:58,730
She's very close to achieving hers now.

634
00:34:58,730 --> 00:34:59,440
Her dream

635
00:34:59,440 --> 00:35:01,100
is only one step away from her.

636
00:35:01,110 --> 00:35:02,920
The result really doesn't matter.

637
00:35:02,920 --> 00:35:04,780
At least she should give it a shot.

638
00:35:05,190 --> 00:35:07,050
I understand what you're saying.

639
00:35:07,980 --> 00:35:09,170
But reality...

640
00:35:09,860 --> 00:35:11,690
isn't as simple as you think.

641
00:35:14,210 --> 00:35:15,540
Speaking of reality...

642
00:35:17,940 --> 00:35:19,420
we don't define

643
00:35:19,510 --> 00:35:20,670
a good life

644
00:35:20,730 --> 00:35:21,940
as having much money

645
00:35:22,280 --> 00:35:23,460
and many houses.

646
00:35:23,860 --> 00:35:24,440
However,

647
00:35:25,420 --> 00:35:27,100
Zhuang Zhuang's mother and I

648
00:35:29,090 --> 00:35:32,010
both hope her future life

649
00:35:32,190 --> 00:35:33,670
can be stable and secure.

650
00:35:34,730 --> 00:35:36,390
That's also part of the reason

651
00:35:36,650 --> 00:35:38,580
for her quitting the competition.

652
00:35:40,050 --> 00:35:42,570
She needs to figure out for herself

653
00:35:43,470 --> 00:35:45,270
which path to take in the future.

654
00:35:46,340 --> 00:35:49,730
Both of you need some alone time.

655
00:35:53,420 --> 00:35:53,950
Shengli,

656
00:35:55,840 --> 00:35:59,360
you are at an age to hustle and grind.

657
00:35:59,530 --> 00:36:01,190
you should focus on doing well

658
00:36:01,420 --> 00:36:02,750
with the things at hand.

659
00:36:03,360 --> 00:36:04,880
As for everything else,

660
00:36:05,570 --> 00:36:08,530
leave it to time and fate.

661
00:37:10,090 --> 00:37:11,150
[Prosperity]

662
00:37:11,150 --> 00:37:14,370
[Hostel]

663
00:37:12,170 --> 00:37:12,780
Ma'am?

664
00:37:14,320 --> 00:37:15,510
Ma'am, I need a room.

665
00:37:16,210 --> 00:37:17,210
For how many days?

666
00:37:17,550 --> 00:37:19,240
Well... three.

667
00:37:20,420 --> 00:37:21,070
Your ID?

668
00:37:36,320 --> 00:37:37,780
Ma'am, can I use the phone?

669
00:37:38,260 --> 00:37:38,780
Sure.

670
00:37:38,900 --> 00:37:40,650
30 cents a minute for local calls,
and 60 for long-distance ones.

671
00:37:40,650 --> 00:37:42,190
Okay, this call is going to Beijing.

672
00:37:42,190 --> 00:37:42,590
Okay.

673
00:37:53,300 --> 00:37:53,570
Hello?

674
00:37:53,570 --> 00:37:54,300
Hello, Manager.

675
00:37:54,300 --> 00:37:55,230
This is Shengli.

676
00:37:55,730 --> 00:37:57,300
Shengli, where are you?

677
00:37:57,380 --> 00:37:58,240
I'm in Wenzhou.

678
00:37:59,050 --> 00:38:00,650
Director Weng is in trouble.

679
00:38:00,840 --> 00:38:01,630
His house under mortgage

680
00:38:01,630 --> 00:38:03,360
has been auctioned by the bank.

681
00:38:10,470 --> 00:38:11,760
My old house...

682
00:38:13,120 --> 00:38:15,650
was auctioned off for over 900,000 yuan.

683
00:38:16,400 --> 00:38:17,650
The 500,000 I owed the bank

684
00:38:17,650 --> 00:38:18,650
has been paid off.

685
00:38:18,800 --> 00:38:20,050
The rest of the money

686
00:38:20,050 --> 00:38:20,880
is in this passbook.

687
00:38:20,880 --> 00:38:23,190
The police have already caught
the culprit.

688
00:38:23,190 --> 00:38:25,320
Although he has squandered
the money,

689
00:38:25,320 --> 00:38:28,110
it's not entirely impossible
to make him compensate.

690
00:38:28,110 --> 00:38:29,530
This won't do, Director Weng.

691
00:38:29,530 --> 00:38:31,030
I can't let you pay for everything alone.

692
00:38:31,030 --> 00:38:31,980
I'll work something out.

693
00:38:31,980 --> 00:38:33,040
No, don't.

694
00:38:33,150 --> 00:38:35,550
I'll by no means let you bear the debt.

695
00:38:37,130 --> 00:38:39,530
Besides, I introduced that guy
to the crew.

696
00:38:39,530 --> 00:38:40,990
I'm also feeling terrible

697
00:38:41,300 --> 00:38:43,160
about how things have turned out.

698
00:38:44,590 --> 00:38:46,900
Plus, you don't have any money.

699
00:38:48,000 --> 00:38:49,390
Anyway, no matter what,

700
00:38:49,460 --> 00:38:50,050
we

701
00:38:50,050 --> 00:38:51,170
did this together.

702
00:38:51,530 --> 00:38:53,860
So I should take half the responsibility.

703
00:39:29,760 --> 00:39:31,740
[The Late Love]

704
00:39:32,470 --> 00:39:33,610
[The Late Love]

705
00:39:39,300 --> 00:39:40,100
Put it inside.

706
00:39:40,380 --> 00:39:40,800
Okay.

707
00:39:40,900 --> 00:39:41,510
How's the flavor?

708
00:39:41,510 --> 00:39:42,420
Good, huh?

709
00:39:42,420 --> 00:39:43,150
Pretty nice.

710
00:39:49,950 --> 00:39:51,410
Too cramp up there, right?

711
00:40:01,940 --> 00:40:02,760
Buddy,

712
00:40:02,790 --> 00:40:05,120
you're reselling goods in Russia, right?

713
00:40:14,260 --> 00:40:17,830
-Welcome!
-Warm welcome!

714
00:40:17,980 --> 00:40:21,870
-Congratulations!
-Heartfelt congratulations!

715
00:40:21,900 --> 00:40:23,760
Winter in Beijing is really long.

716
00:40:24,750 --> 00:40:26,660
Spring is approaching, isn't it?

717
00:40:27,710 --> 00:40:28,530
Shengli,

718
00:40:29,650 --> 00:40:31,770
Zhuang Zhuang can't go with you.

719
00:40:32,170 --> 00:40:33,980
Zhuang Zhuang's mother and I

720
00:40:35,890 --> 00:40:37,030
both hope

721
00:40:37,430 --> 00:40:38,620
her future life

722
00:40:39,090 --> 00:40:40,530
can be stable and secure.

723
00:40:41,430 --> 00:40:42,910
That's part of the reason

724
00:40:43,460 --> 00:40:45,390
for her quitting the competition.

725
00:40:46,900 --> 00:40:49,620
She needs to figure out for herself

726
00:40:50,400 --> 00:40:52,200
which path to take in the future.

727
00:40:53,360 --> 00:40:56,460
Both of you need some alone time.

728
00:41:12,450 --> 00:41:15,210
[Central TV & Radio Tower;
altitude: 405 meters]

729
00:41:32,000 --> 00:41:33,670
The surgery was very successful.

730
00:41:33,670 --> 00:41:35,580
The patient can be transferred
to a regular ward tonight.

731
00:41:34,420 --> 00:41:39,630
[No smoking in public areas]

732
00:41:36,460 --> 00:41:37,400
Every time you turn her over,

733
00:41:37,400 --> 00:41:38,840
check on the drainage tube.

734
00:41:38,840 --> 00:41:40,320
If the fluid turns bright red,

735
00:41:40,320 --> 00:41:41,690
the volume suddenly increases,

736
00:41:41,690 --> 00:41:43,130
or the flow is blocked by blood clots,

737
00:41:43,130 --> 00:41:44,430
turn to a nurse immediately.

738
00:41:44,390 --> 00:41:49,040
[No smoking in public areas]

739
00:41:44,570 --> 00:41:45,880
Okay. Thanks for your hard work.

740
00:41:45,880 --> 00:41:46,340
Thank you.

741
00:41:46,340 --> 00:41:47,000
No problem.

742
00:41:49,380 --> 00:41:51,180
I'll watch your mother tonight.

743
00:41:51,570 --> 00:41:53,260
You haven't slept for days.

744
00:41:53,320 --> 00:41:54,320
Go get some sleep.

745
00:41:54,380 --> 00:41:55,980
Try not to worry your mother.

746
00:41:56,960 --> 00:41:58,760
I want to make a trip to Shanghai.

747
00:41:59,400 --> 00:42:01,800
You still want to find a specialist
for her?

748
00:42:01,960 --> 00:42:02,690
My mom already has

749
00:42:02,690 --> 00:42:03,940
underlying endocrine conditions

750
00:42:03,940 --> 00:42:06,400
that'll affect her recovery after surgery.

751
00:42:07,190 --> 00:42:09,330
I'm worried that missing
the best recovery window

752
00:42:09,330 --> 00:42:11,860
will increase her risk
of cancer recurrence.

753
00:42:12,210 --> 00:42:14,340
We need to get her in a better hospital.

754
00:42:16,550 --> 00:42:16,960
Okay.

755
00:42:17,480 --> 00:42:18,080
Thank you.

756
00:42:19,730 --> 00:42:21,390
Sweaters, quality sweaters!

757
00:42:21,960 --> 00:42:23,090
Quality sweaters!

758
00:42:23,900 --> 00:42:24,570
This is good stuff.

759
00:42:24,570 --> 00:42:25,280
Are you Chinese?

760
00:42:25,280 --> 00:42:27,010
This is pretty. Why not buy one?

761
00:42:27,880 --> 00:42:28,810
Lower the price?

762
00:42:29,110 --> 00:42:31,240
I'm already selling at the cost price.

763
00:42:36,500 --> 00:42:36,920
This.

764
00:42:37,860 --> 00:42:38,420
H-How about this one?

765
00:42:38,420 --> 00:42:38,980
No, no.

766
00:42:39,250 --> 00:42:39,780
That one.

767
00:42:41,470 --> 00:42:42,400
Are you Chinese?

768
00:42:43,340 --> 00:42:43,940
Sweaters.

769
00:42:44,400 --> 00:42:45,070
Lovely sweaters.
